</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/644ae690160e658898a141e568a7fb0ee6040004" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -0.338ex; width:1.056ex; height:1.676ex;" alt="\mathbf {s} "></span>.  In our problem, we know <span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle \mathbf {c} }">
